In Search of a Midnight Kiss;;79;;85;;NC;;Following the worst 12 months of his life, a 29-year-old man ends up alone and penniless as New Year's Eve rapidly approaches, and vows to lock his doors, pull his blinds, and climb into bed - until his best friend talks him into posting a Craigslist personal ad. In seemingly no time at all, the message leads him to a young woman who is determined to be with the "right" man at the stroke of midnight.;;Romance,Comedy;;Alex Holdridge;;2007;;Scoot McNairy,Sara Simmonds,Brian Matthew McGuire,Kathleen Luong,Bret Roberts,Twink Caplan,Robert Murphy;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/in_search_of_a_midnight_kiss